                      Elaborate <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐረግ፡</foreign> using some or all of the following:
                      black, red, yellow and brown <locus target="#1r #6v #13r #20r #28r #34r #38v #45v #54r #60r #64v #74r #82v #84v #94r #110r #118v" facs="003 010 016 023 031 037 042 049 057 063 068 077 086 097 113 122">folss. 1r, 6v, 13r, 20r, 28r, 34r, 38v, 45v, 54r, 60r, 64v, 74r, 82v, 84v, 94r, 110r, 118v, </locus>.
                      Line of alternating red and black dots as section divider <locus target="#1r #27v #28v #33v #89r #94r #104r #109v #110v #116v #117v #118v" facs="003 031 032 037 092 097 107 113 120 121 122">folss. 1r, 27v, 28v, 33v, 89r, 94r, 104r, 109v, 110v, 116v, 117v, 118v, </locus>.
                      Multiple full-stop symbols <locus target="#115v" facs="119">fol. 115v</locus>
